node.text: @lykkeli and I r doing this tomorrow in support of  @berniesanders - if you are in Las Vegas come by. if you want to see America become a kinder place where we work to make life better for all of us, Get Up Get Into It and Get Involved

I want to extend a warm THANK YOU to all the wonderful weirdos I’ve had the pleasure of collaborating with this last decade. Feeling alot of love for you all today and for the jams we kicked out. Here are some selected records I’ve been blessed to’ve been a part of 2009-2019.  And here’s to 2020 y’all some of the best music we’ve made this decade hasn’t been released yet ;) 🥂 🖤 ❤️AW
